commit.message:
Merge pull request #2 from anatol/patch-1

Add license to gemspec
[BUGFIX] Don't apply nil namespace prefixes to attributes
Ensure that all namespaces are inherited from nodes
Allow writing attributes with converter methods
[BUGFIX] Inherit children which don't respond to #namespace

[BUGFIX] Inheriting nodes should copy namespaces on child nodes explicitly

Fixes JRuby
[BUGFIX] Some namespace related bugs on JRuby
[CS] Set the document root in Node specs

[BUGFIX] Set the namespace when inheriting more correctly

* Allow nokogiri to do its usual checking

[UPDATE] Relax the Nokogiri dependency to 1.x

* We still have a spec failure on Nokogiri 1.5, but it should be fixed upstream: https://github.com/tenderlove/nokogiri/issues/647

Merge pull request #1 from taylor/master

Fixed Jruby build
